s好似limited to 1MB, 起碼大過Twitter嗰140-character limit嘅，但用嚟裝posts, 好似唔多够。"},{"pid":"edc69a44a6395ee4e400b1123d5808966c20aeab","tid":404333,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔清楚技術細節 但bitcoin blockchain記錄既資訊好少 例如得交易資料 時間 用家等等<br />\n如果要做forum 要儲存既係好多好多文字 唔單單係integer 可以做到<br />\n到時讀取速度又可能係好大個樽頸位</blockquote><br />\nBlocks好似limited to 1MB, 起碼大過Twitter嗰140-character limit嘅，但用嚟裝posts, 好似唔多够。</blockquote><br />\n純文字夠曬啦，再加埋replyto而唔係攞曬所有舊post文字再出多次"},{"pid":"46ad93509cd198893406848a4bd9f56e8b5e658b","tid":404333,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔清楚技術細節 但bitcoin blockchain記錄既資訊好少 例如得交易資料 時間 用家等等<br />\n如果要做forum 要儲存既係好多好多文字 唔單單係integer 可以做到<br />\n到時讀取速度又可能係好大個樽頸位</blockquote><br />\nBlocks好似limited to 1MB, 起碼大過Twitter嗰140-character limit嘅，但用嚟裝posts, 好似唔多够。</blockquote><br />\n純文字夠曬啦，再加埋replyto而唔係攞曬所有舊post文字再出多次</blockquote><br />\nAnyway, blockchain都唔太relevant, 其實就咁起個real-time backup server已經解決到問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4c197f9c57a6bc2d87908c522e6bcf65963e38","tid":404333,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"blocks limit 係可以更改<br />\n但block chain 安全性係靠算力多少來維持，就算個技術work，對於個人來講成本太高。 <br />\n除非個論壇所有廣告收入可以按算力多少分比願意做node既人，就可能可以一玩。 可以玩到 發貼都要收個點數，會員又可以相互donate，強逼D人做node來維護呢個forum。<br />\n申利: 8 張display card 等你地 寫出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f6bbe6d648f57aba4e929e37c860905199c132","tid":404333,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"吹水冇難度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/329941/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/329941/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"42d7709be143ff959c6324171804162f78097e7d","tid":404333,"uid":1573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited